"title": "5340: house",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5340",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The place where someone lives. Its extended use includes a household and dynasty and its figurative use includes the house of God and heaven.</p>\n<h2>The construction of houses</h2>\n<h3>Foundations</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:17\">1KI 5:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra6:3-Ezra6:4\">EZR 6:3–6:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer51:26\">JER 51:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek41:8\">EZK 41:8</a></p>\n<h3>Building materials</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen11:3-Gen11:4\">GEN 11:3–11:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod1:11-Exod1:14\">EXO 1:11–1:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:40-Lev14:45\">LEV 14:40–14:45</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs5:18\">1KI 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:9-1Kgs7:12\">1KI 7:9–7:12</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song1:17\">SNG 1:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:10\">ISA 9:10</a></p>\n<h3>Rooms and decoration</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen43:30\">GEN 43:30</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:20\">JDG 3:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:23-Judg3:25\">JDG 3:23–3:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs7:6\">1KI 7:6</a> <em>Solomon's palace</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs17:19\">1KI 17:19</a> <em>Elijah stays with the widow at Zarephath</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs22:25\">1KI 22:25</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs1:2\">2KI 1:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs4:10\">2KI 4:10</a> <em>Elisha's room at the Shunammite's house</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh8:16\">NEH 8:16</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer22:14\">JER 22:14</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek8:10\">EZK 8:10</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:5\">DAN 5:5</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos3:15\">AMO 3:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:8-Acts20:9\">ACT 20:8–20:9</a></p>\n<h3>Roofs</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:6\">JOS 2:6</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam9:25-1Sam9:26\">1SA 9:25–9:26</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark2:4\">MRK 2:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke5:19\">LUK 5:19</a></p>\n<h2>Regulations regarding houses</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev14:33-Lev14:53\">LEV 14:33–14:53</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:29-Lev25:34\">LEV 25:29–25:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev27:14-Lev27:15\">LEV 27:14–27:15</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut22:8\">DEU 22:8</a></p>\n<h2>Various uses for houses</h2>\n<h3>House arrest</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer37:15\">JER 37:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen40:2-Gen40:3\">GEN 40:2–40:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam20:3\">2SA 20:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:16\">ACT 28:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts28:30-Acts28:31\">ACT 28:30–28:31</a></p>\n<h3>Church gatherings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col4:15\">COL 4:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts1:13-Acts1:14\">ACT 1:13–1:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts2:1-Acts2:2\">ACT 2:1–2:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:42\">ACT 5:42</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:12\">ACT 12:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:5\">ROM 16:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:19\">1CO 16:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phlm1:1-Phlm1:2\">PHM 1:1–1:2</a></p>\n<h2>Parables and proverbs about houses</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:20\">PRO 21:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:1-Prov9:4\">PRO 9:1–9:4</a> <em>the house of wisdom</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov9:13-Prov9:18\">PRO 9:13–9:18</a> <em>the house of folly</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov14:1\">PRO 14:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:13\">PRO 17:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov21:9\">PRO 21:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov24:27\">PRO 24:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov25:17\">PRO 25:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl10:18\">ECC 10:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Song8:7\">SNG 8:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:29\">MAT 12:29</a> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark3:27\">MRK 3:27</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:21-Luke11:22\">LUK 11:21–11:22</a> <em>plundering the strong man's house</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:43-Matt12:45\">MAT 12:43–12:45</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke11:24-Luke11:26\">LUK 11:24–11:26</a> <em>the return of evil spirits to an unoccupied house</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt13:52\">MAT 13:52</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:42-Matt24:51\">MAT 24:42–24:51</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:39-Luke12:46\">LUK 12:39–12:46</a></p>\n<h2>The house of God</h2>\n<h3>God's heavenly dwelling</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:1-Isa66:2\">ISA 66:1–66:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:30\">1KI 8:30</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:21\">2CH 6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:39\">1KI 8:39</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:30\">2CH 6:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:43\">1KI 8:43</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:33\">2CH 6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:49-1Kgs8:50\">1KI 8:49–8:50</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr6:39\">2CH 6:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:2\">JHN 14:2</a></p>\n<h3>The earthly tabernacle and temple</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:8\">EXO 25:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod15:17\">EXO 15:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod29:44-Exod29:46\">EXO 29:44–29:46</a> <em>the Tent of Meeting</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:5\">DEU 12:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut12:11\">DEU 12:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:1-2Sam7:7\">2SA 7:1–7:7</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:1-1Chr17:6\">1CH 17:1–17:6</a> <em>David's desire to build a permanent house for God to dwell in</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezra5:13-Ezra5:16\">EZR 5:13–5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:6\">PSA 23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps26:8\">PSA 26:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:4\">PSA 27:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:1-Ps84:4\">PSA 84:1–84:4</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:10\">PSA 84:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:2-Hag1:3\">HAG 1:2–1:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:8-Hag1:9\">HAG 1:8–1:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:14\">HAG 1:14</a></p>\n<h2>The household</h2>\n<h3>Household affairs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam17:23\">2SA 17:23</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:1\">2KI 20:1</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa38:1\">ISA 38:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:21\">PRO 31:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov31:27\">PRO 31:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:4-1Tim3:5\">1TI 3:4–3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:12\">1TI 3:12</a></p>\n<h3>Examples of how God relates to households</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:12-Gen17:14\">GEN 17:12–17:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen17:23-Gen17:27\">GEN 17:23–17:27</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:6\">LEV 16:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:11\">LEV 16:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev16:17\">LEV 16:17</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num16:31-Num16:33\">NUM 16:31–16:33</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:53\">JHN 4:53</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:15\">ACT 16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts16:31-Acts16:34\">ACT 16:31–16:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:15\">1CO 16:15</a></p>\n<h3>The church as God's household</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:19-Eph2:22\">EPH 2:19–2:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:7\">NUM 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:14-1Tim3:15\">1TI 3:14–3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:1-Heb3:6\">HEB 3:1–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:4-1Pet2:5\">1PE 2:4–2:5</a></p>\n<h2>House in the sense of a dynasty</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:16\">2SA 7:16</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:14\">1CH 17:14</a> <em>“house” is used here in the sense of “royal house” or “dynasty”.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod40:38\">EXO 40:38</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh21:43-Josh21:451\">JOS 21:43–21:451</a>SA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh2:27-Josh2:36\">2:27–2:36</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:11-1Sam3:142\">1SA 3:11–3:142</a>SA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam3:1\">3:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam9:1\">2SA 9:1</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam3:28-2Sam3:292\">2SA 3:28–3:292</a>SA <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Sam7:25-2Sam7:29\">7:25–7:29</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr17:23-1Chr17:27\">1CH 17:23–17:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:31-1Kgs2:33\">1KI 2:31–2:33</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:21-1Kgs21:22\">1KI 21:21–21:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs21:28-1Kgs21:29\">1KI 21:28–21:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech12:10-Zech12:14\">ZEC 12:10–12:14</a></p>",
